#ROOMS
#16253
Chamber of the Dawnshadow~
A simple chamber made of a shadowy substance with a window
overlooking outside it, revealing a field of roses glowing the color
of flame. One climbs the edge of a bookcase, finely crafted and
filled with books and scrolls. A tapestry holds the story of the
Dawnshadow, written in kanji on rice paper, carefully illustrating
his doom. A being with black wings casting a red dagger, whilst
a warrior casts a gold and a wave of black magic and white fire.
There are two chairs beside a fireplace, high backed yet padded
and comfortable, and a comfortable bed. A small table with several
wineglasses filled with a glowing liquid... wine made of the necter
of the glowing roses. Above the bed is a portrait of a man's face, pale
and powerful, commanding of presence. A scar marrs his right cheek,
and his black eyes are swarmed with a violet mist. Black hair with a touch
of violet flows down beside his head. On the black gold frame is engraved
Night Lord Mercury. On either side of this portrait hang two sabres,
identical, floating as if by magic. Black blades and hilts, they hold a single
ruby in each, carved perfectly in the shape of a raven.
~
