#16254
Realm of Shadows~
A simple chamber of a gently dark beauty, flaming flowers adorning the
walls to cast what light there is. An open window shows the gentle light
of a smooth white orb that casts as much light as the full moon. It seems
to have a strange calmness to it, a gentle safety. One wall is covered
entirely in kanji and images. There is a history here, of blood and violence,
and of love and healing. Several names stand out in particular. Karci....
Kali.... Dulcea.... Moyra.... Jisa..... Jasin..... Lendarion.... Emerath. And near
the bottom, one final name engraved in silver .... Aerin.
~
